InterAACtion Web
================

InterAACtion Web is a derivative of AFSR/InterAACtionBox.

Upstream project:
  https://github.com/AFSR/InterAACtionBox
  Copyright (c) Association Française du Syndrome de Rett (AFSR)
                and the InterAACtionBox contributors.

This repository was seeded via a mirror clone on 2026-04-24, so the commit
history from upstream is preserved, including attribution of all original
contributors. Two paths were stripped from the historical objects before
publication:

  - Libs/                       (bundled Ubuntu/Tobii/TeamViewer .deb packages
                                 irrelevant to a web build; removed to keep
                                 the repository a reasonable size)
  - Ressources/google-chrome/   (a pre-seeded Chrome profile that contained
                                 residual session credentials; removed for
                                 security reasons)

No commit authorship, message, or ordering was altered.

